snippet.textDisplay: I never ever want this song to be popular, this is something very close to my heart. The time when this song released, my soul was shattering piece by piece every other day so I dedicated this to me in those broken heart days. I don’t want anybody to discover this song, i am so much possessive for this. Specially when he sings, “kisi nu ki kehna yari aapay mein laayi”. Thanks Shiraz , thanks Kashif and specially Rachel.
